         <div type="translation" xml:lang="ru">
            <p>Сотерих (жрец ?) богини Девы, проживший 80 лет и его супруга Конха, прожившая ...
               лет.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
            <p>Soterichos (priest?) of Goddess Parthenos, having lived 80 years, and his wife Koncha,
               having lived ... years.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary" xml:lang="ru">
            <p>"Quomodo genetivi θεᾶς Παρθένου explicandi sint, non satis liquet : possunt pendere a
               subaudienda vel fortasse per errorem omissa voce ἱερεύς , sed possunt etiam pro</p>
            <p>genetivis possesivis accipi, ut intellegamus Soterichus Virginis ἱεροδούλος fuisse"
               (IOSPE I2).</p>
         </div>
